v.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/NTDM/111%2c%e8%81%b2%2c226%2c20220602%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"NTDM,111,聲,226,20220602,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"226","JDATE":"20220602","JTITLE":"定應執行刑"}